{"tid":968612,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"冰冰40年前辣照曝光 網驚呼：神似周子瑜","createTime":"2019-01-04T11:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T12:29:28.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":547,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"71cb27725c95c850136fbbea90fd7bc3b8a6c374","tid":968612,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-01-04/656/20190104001899.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-01-04%2F656%2F20190104001899.jpg&h=bf092562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白冰冰40年前辣照被網友搜出曝光，讓眾人直呼辣翻了。<br />\n<br />\n藝人白冰冰受高雄觀光局邀請，擔任一月高雄代言人，未料卻引發爭議，甚至遭丁允恭砲轟毀掉質感，而國民黨發言人洪孟楷則跳出來護航，直言「白冰冰可能是三十年前的周子瑜」，立刻引起網友討論，而PTT鄉民更挖出白冰冰40年前舊照，紛紛表示：「真的有辣到」。<br />\n<br />\n有網友拿出周子瑜的照片對比，直呼兩人神韻有點神似，此外還有人搜出白冰冰40年前在日本出道時的宣傳照，只見她身穿著白色半截上衣並露出肚子，下半身則是穿著白色小褲，打拳踢腿的姿勢差點讓私密部位走光，可說是讓人看得臉紅心跳。"},{"pid":"c4f5c7eba20831e81c47b8e62de5f916e696ea83","tid":968612,"uid":223790,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T11:05:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"865f68225f84c0244e61e24f0a86e5b1204964bb","tid":968612,"uid":223790,"like":333,"dislike":2,"score":331,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1d26dbc65394be7c9bb2651b261e9e00e0c6822","tid":968612,"uid":223790,"like":67,"dislike":49,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T11:05:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"729afe2ef25f325345c7f1db9ea7aa67941acd72","tid":968612,"uid":108993,"like":284,"dislike":1,"score":283,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T11:06:07.000Z","msg":"邊撚到似<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c052a94dad2dda786c32ac3fb0c5751c251d78fc","tid":968612,"uid":223790,"like":6,"dislike":23,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T11:06:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"011075fcb7f0643bb26c57170e7b85a598ce71cb","tid":968612,"uid":179630,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-